<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.6">
<l>tāyāy vanta pēyuyirun tayirum viḻutu muṭaṉuṇṭa</l>
<l>vāyāṉ tūya variyuruviṟ kuṟaḷāyc ceṉṟu māvaliyai</l>
<l>ēyā ṉirappa mūvaṭimaṇ ṇiṉṟe tāveṉ ṟulakēḻum</l>
<l>tāyāṉ kāyā malarvaṇṇaṉ cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge in Śālagrāma of the one the color of kāyā buds,</l>
<l>The one whose mouth consumed butter together with curds</l>
<l rend="indent">and the life of the demoness who came [disguised] as his mother,</l>
<l>Who, arriving as a pure and beautifully formed dwarf,</l>
<l rend="indent">deceived Māvali,</l>
<l>The one who, as he begged saying “Now give [me] three feet of earth,”</l>
<l rend="indent">leapt over the seven worlds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
